# Open features

## Save All / Load Project / Reset
Not started. Design decisions still pending:
- ProjectStateManager class
- saveProject() — bundle all scene JSONs + referenced assets into a packaged file (proposed: .ttrpg, internally ZIP)
- loadProject() — replace current data/ + assets/ with unpacked contents; warn before overwrite
- resetProject() — wipe everything, create a fresh default scene
- Menu items: File → Save Project / Load Project… / Reset Project
- Safety UX: overwrite warning on save, confirmation + backup suggestion on reset

## Named log sessions
Low priority. When enabling logging, optionally prompt for a human-readable session name
(e.g. "Session 5 — Dragon Cave") to use as the folder name instead of the raw timestamp.
No code changes needed until this is prioritised.

## Browse for music from any location
Currently the music file picker is restricted to assets/music/.
Allow browsing anywhere on disk and normalise the selected path to relative if possible.

## Audio device selection
JavaFX MediaPlayer does not expose device selection without a third-party library.
Likely out of scope unless a library is adopted.
